                    </svg>
                    <div class="flex flex-col text-left">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-white">Community Hub</span>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Join the Discord</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <section class="w-full max-w-md mb-12">
            <h2 class="stranger-things-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-6">Discord Status</h2>
            <DiscordPresence userId="1000470631688712243" />
        </section>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <section class="w-full max-w-2xl mb-12">
            <h2 class="stranger-things-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-6">About Me</h2>
            <div class="card text-left">
                <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                    Welcome to my corner of the internet! I'm TazElite, a passionate gamer and content creator
                    who loves bringing people together through gaming. Whether I'm streaming the latest titles
                    or building an awesome community on Discord, my goal is to create a fun and welcoming space
                    for everyone.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
                    Come hang out, watch some streams, and join our growing community. Let's game together!
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="w-full max-w-2xl mb-12">
            <h2 class="stranger-things-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-6">What I Do</h2>
